ËÙµU<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";s:368:"<p>Research evidence to date has shown that ACT can assist people with a range of psychological problems, including depression, anxiety (including obsessive compulsive disorder and posttraumatic stress disorder), stress, pain, eating disorders, addictions, and psychosis. ACT has been shown to be effective for individuals and couples, as well as in group therapy.</p>";}